         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">6 April 1880. ¶ Mr Moritz Holtze ¶ Port Darwin ¶  ¶ After careful examination I see, dear fellow countryman, that your grass No. 4 is  ¶ Panicum gibbosum ¶  R. Br. in a very fine and slender form. Nr....</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">80.04.06</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Maurice Holtze</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">GRG 19/391, State records of South Australia, Adelaide.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">6/4/80</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Herrn Moritz Holtze.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Port Darwin.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Nach genauer Untersuchung sehe ich, lieber Herr Landsmann, dass Ihr Gras N. 4. <name key="Panicum%20gibbosum">Panicum gibbosum</name> R. Br. in einer sehr dünnen u schlanken Form ist. N. 13 = <name key="Ipomoea%20angustifolia">Ipomoea angustifolia</name> Jacquin.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihr Pittosporum wird wohl mein P. melanospermum sein, doch muss die Frucht dies entscheiden. Ich rathe Ihnen die Samen dieses schönen Bäumchens zu vertheilen. Wahrscheinlich sind die Blumen wohlriechend?</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Dieser Brief war verlegt; doch sende ich ihn verspätet ab.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mit besten Wünschen für Ihr Wohlergehen</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">6 April 1880.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Mr Moritz Holtze</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Port Darwin</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>After careful examination I see, dear fellow countryman, that your grass No. 4 is <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Panicum%20gibbosum">Panicum gibbosum</name>
               </seg> R. Br. in a very fine and slender form. Nr. 13 is <name key="Ipomoea%20angustifolia">Ipomoea angustifolia</name> Jacquin.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See list, M to M. Holtze, 1880 (in this edition as 80-04-00d), nos. 4, 13.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Pittosporum</seg> will probably be my <seg style="font-style: italic; ">P. melanospermum</seg>,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See list, M to M. Holtze, 1880 (in this edition as 80-04-00d), no. 6.</p>
               </note> but only the fruit can determine this. I advise you to distribute seeds of this beautiful little tree. I surmise that the flowers are probably perfumed?</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>This letter had been mislaid; but I am sending it belatedly.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With best wishes for your welfare,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Ipomoea%20angustifolia">Ipomoea angustifolia</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Panicum%20gibbosum">Panicum gibbosum</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Pittosporum%20melanospermum">Pittosporum melanospermum</name>
            </p>
         </div>
